# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

"Frog Chess"


## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A two-player chess game that has a special new piece, a frog, that moves by jumping over its own player's pieces.


## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

My software will be able to have two players play against each other in chess. Each player will be able to choose their every move, and it will keep track of lost pieces and decide who wins the game. It will have the unique frog piece that moves by jumping over that player's own pieces, and takes other pieces by landing on them. It can jump over pieces in any direction. If none of the player's pieces are rin a space right next to it, then the frog cannot move. I will execute this game using Pygame.


